{"article_id":"ekVwzmciWxttCABy","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Speaking to reporters briefly at the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Donald Trump repeated the most consequential of the many lies of his presidency","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that the federal government did a \" fantastic job \" in its response to last year ' s Hurricane Maria catastrophe","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that killed nearly 3,000 people in Puerto Rico .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Trump defends the government response in Puerto Rico","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the day","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"after Puerto Rico raised its death toll from Hurricane Maria to 2,975 .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"we did a fantastic job in Puerto Rico ...","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"I think","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"most of the people in Puerto Rico really appreciate what we 've done . ''","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"( via ABC )","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"pic.twitter.com/r3K2ylTB9w","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"- Kyle Griffin","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"( @ kylegriffin1 )","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"August 29 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"That ' s a line","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that Trump has maintained","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"ever since he made a belated visit to the island","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"after two straight weekends golfing ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"followed by the observation","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that \" it ' s been incredible the results","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that we ' ve had with respect to loss of life . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"In fact , the results","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"they had","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"with respect to the loss of life were awful .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Awful in terms of the sheer number of dead ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"but also awful in terms of the reluctance from the very beginning","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to deliver an accurate death count .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"That the disaster turned out to be deadlier even than Hurricane Katrina is shocking ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"and the fact","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that it took the government until this week to finally acknowledge that fact","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"is an entirely separate shock .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"And it ' s a reminder","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"while Trump ' s time in office has shown","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that the macroeconomy can remain remarkably robust in the face of a president","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"who has no idea what he ' s doing ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"there are other aspects of national affairs where this is not the case .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Trump is a president","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"who can ' t even properly execute a relatively simple presidential task","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"like leading the national mourning for the late Sen. John McCain in an appropriate way .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Faced with something genuinely difficult like a strong hurricane","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"hitting an island","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"whose electrical infrastructure was already in rocky shape ,","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"he just totally failed with catastrophic consequences .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Trump ' s instinct from Day 1 has been to simply turn the island ' s devastation into another front in culture-war politics , a strategy","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that has helped keep his political career alive","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"despite his lack of substantive command of the job .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"The rest of us just have to pray for good luck .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"That Trump spends an almost inhuman amount of time","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"watching cable television","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"is something","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"we now all take for granted as part of the background noise of our lives .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"What ' s often forgotten is the role","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump ' s preference for television over proper briefings played","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"in creating the crisis .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"But back in 2017 , Hurricanes Harvey and Irma were massive cable television events","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"that dominated coverage on all the networks .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Hurricane Maria , by contrast , was relatively invisible on cable ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"according to reporting from Dhrumil Mehta at FiveThirtyEight .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"\" People on TV news shows spoke significantly fewer sentences about Hurricane Maria than about Hurricanes Harvey and Irma , \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"he writes ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"and \" the spike in conversation about Puerto Rico","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"right as the hurricane hit","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"was also much smaller than the spike in mentions of Texas and Florida . \"","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Cable producers surely had their reasons for this .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"But something","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"anyone in the media could tell you","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"is that cable producers ' news judgment is not an infallible guide to the substantive importance of various stories .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"In particular , a broad range of issues","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"- potentially including natural disasters in outlying US territories -","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"have an asymmetrical quality to them .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"If handled appropriately ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"most people won ' t care that much ;","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"but","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"if botched ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"it eventually becomes a big deal .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"This is why presidents have traditionally relied upon staff and the massive information-gathering capabilities of the American government for information","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"rather than letting television set the agenda .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"Trump has a different philosophy , however ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and spent the post-storm Saturday glued to his television","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and letting the hosts of Fox & Friends drag him into an ill-advised Twitter spat with NBA star Steph Curry and various NFL players .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"`` Fox & Friends '' covered this story at 8:24am .","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"Banner :","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` Curry Wants to Skip White House Visit . ''","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Trump tweeted at 8:45.","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"https : //t.co/hVN7qnRwyy","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"- Brian Stelter","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"( @ brianstelter )","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"September 23 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Because Trump wasn ' t paying attention ,","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"the situation evolved into a catastrophe .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"because the situation evolved into a catastrophe ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"it eventually ended up on television .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"The Washington Post reports","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"that by Monday , Trump \" was becoming frustrated by the coverage","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"he was seeing on TV . \"","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"By the time Trump ' s sluggish response became a national issue ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"the White House was full of excuses .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"Trump emphasized in public remarks last fall","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"that Puerto Rico is \" an island","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"surrounded by water , \"","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"which makes relief difficult .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"An anonymous administration official told the Washington Post","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"that \" the Department of Defense , FEMA and the federal government are having to step in","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"to fulfill state and municipal functions","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"that we normally just support . \"","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Officials have also cited the Posse Comitatus Act as a complicating factor","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that helps explain","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"why Trump was so much slower to dispatch assistance to Puerto Rico","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"than the Obama administration was to send help to Haiti","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"after it was devastated by an earthquake in 2010 .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Last but by no means least , the reality is that this was a really big disaster .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"The storm was huge and powerful ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"and it knocked out electricity and communications","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"- that ' s hard to deal with .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"This is all true ,","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"and it goes to show that being president of the United States is a difficult job .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"But all of the issues","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"that the federal response is wrestling with","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"were known in advance .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"The world had days of warning","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"that a hurricane was heading toward Puerto Rico .","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"The perilous state of the island ' s electrical grid has been apparent for years","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"- as has the weak financial health of its electrical utility and municipal governments .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"A president","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"who was focused on his job","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"could have asked in advance what the plan was for a hurricane strike on Puerto Rico .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"He would have discovered","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":133,"text":"since Puerto Rico is part of the United States ,","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"FEMA is the default lead agency ,","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"but it ' s the US military that has the ships and helicopters","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"that would be needed","depth":15},{"id":137,"text":"to get supplies into the interior of a wrecked island .","depth":15},{"id":138,"text":"And he could have worked something out .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Instead , he didn ' t get worked up about Puerto Rico until more than a week after the storm hit ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"when he saw the mayor of San Juan lambasting him on television .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"He lashed out with his usual playbook -","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"one","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"that will only make things worse .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"The substantive problem","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"that Trump","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"- and America -","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"is now facing","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"is that you can ' t go back in time","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"and do the preparatory work","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"that should have been done .","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"You can ' t pre-position satellite phones ,","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"schedule timely visits from top administration officials ,","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"or quickly dispatch ships and helicopters","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"once you ' re starting with an eight-day lag .","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"The best","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"you can do","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"is admit","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"you were too slow","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"and throw everything","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"you ' ve got at it .","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"Defensiveness and counterpunching are .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"So","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"instead of fixing things ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"Trump got into a fight with the mayor of San Juan","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"and inflected his attacks on her with some ugly racial implications .","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"... Such poor leadership ability by the Mayor of San Juan , and others in Puerto Rico ,","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"who are not able to get their workers to help .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"They ....","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":13},{"id":170,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"... want everything to be done for them","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"when it should be a community effort .","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"10,000 Federal workers now on Island","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"doing a fantastic job .","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"September 30 , 2017","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"The Puerto Rico debate then got embroiled in America ' s ongoing debate","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"over whether the real problem is the president being racist ,","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"or liberals being too eager to accuse white people of racism .","depth":9},{"id":182,"text":"Since most Americans are white","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"- and since white people are overrepresented among voters ,","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"and white voters are further overrepresented in the congressional map -","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"this political argument over racism arguably helps Trump politically ,","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"and thus solved the political downside","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"to having botched the response to a huge disaster .","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"Now , nearly a year later , Trump just insists","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"that everything is fine ,","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"as if the sheer force of denial can make problems go away .","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"In the intervening months , we ' ve seen the botched implementation of the cruel family separation policy , a tariff war with China","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"that has no clear goals ,","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"a weird international crisis","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"related to Montenegro ' s NATO membership ,","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"an inability","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"to get the White House flags flown at half-staff","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"to recognize the death of a war hero senator ,","depth":13},{"id":198,"text":"and dozens of other examples of an administration","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"that simply isn ' t up to doing the job","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"it was hired to do .","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"To a perhaps surprising extent , it turns out that the basic machinery of the American government continues to more or less function under these circumstances ,","depth":8},{"id":202,"text":"and with some reasonable people","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"tapped","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"to run the Federal Reserve ,","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"the national economy manages to keep chugging along nicely as well .","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"But things happen in life","depth":8},{"id":207,"text":"- sometimes very bad things -","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"that test a president ' s mettle ,","depth":7},{"id":209,"text":"and we saw in Puerto Rico that Trump isn ' t up to the test .","depth":6},{"id":210,"text":"Bismarck supposedly said","depth":6},{"id":211,"text":"that God has a special providence for fools , drunks , and the United States of America .","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"If we ' re lucky ,","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"he ' ll be proven right ,","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"and nothing much else bad will happen for the next three years .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"If not ,","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"buckle your seat belts .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":433,"left":26